		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A little late now, but for reference:<br /><a href="http://www.midi.org/techspecs/electrispec.php" class="postlink">http://www.midi.org/techspecs/electrispec.php</a><br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">The MIDI IN connector is supposed to have the opto-isolator and no ground connection to pin 2 or to the shield for the express purpose of avoiding a ground loop. </div>

		

